DOC.brief_summary: A Registry to monitor long term safety in female subjects after treatment with Macrolane VRF20 and/or MacrolaneT VRF30 in the breasts.
DOC.criteria: 1. Females previously treated with Macrolane VRF in the breasts 2. Females continuously being treated with Macrolane VRF in the breasts, initial treatment or retreatment. No exclusion criteria
